---
title: Spider Web Bacon and Veg Soup with warm baguette and creme fraiche
description: A spider-themed soup that's sensationally spooky and devilishly delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R24_W43_IE_IEVCLV28045-6_Main_high-40a9f6f3.jpg
